WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:02.389
Good morning, family. How y'all been doing?

00:00:02.399 --> 00:00:04.110
I'm doing good. I just wanted to come

00:00:04.120 --> 00:00:06.430
on and tell you all some

00:00:06.440 --> 00:00:08.150
things that the Lord has been having

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:10.549
me pray over. When I got in

00:00:10.559 --> 00:00:12.509
prayer, this is one of the things that he

00:00:12.519 --> 00:00:14.110
told me. He

00:00:14.120 --> 00:00:18.470
said, "I want you to watch Passover, for

00:00:18.480 --> 00:00:22.910
Passover will become a time of even more

00:00:22.910 --> 00:00:22.920
acceleration."There

00:00:22.920 --> 00:00:25.550
will be an even

00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:27.630
greater

00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:30.150
acceleration at the time of

00:00:30.150 --> 00:00:30.160
Passover.

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:32.269
And then I said,

00:00:32.279 --> 00:00:35.389
"Acceleration of what?"He said, "My son's

00:00:35.399 --> 00:00:39.430
return for the bride is

00:00:39.430 --> 00:00:39.440
imminent."I

00:00:39.440 --> 00:00:41.590
got so excited because the power of God

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:43.950
hit me so strong when he said this.

00:00:43.960 --> 00:00:48.110
He said, "My son's return for the bride is

00:00:48.120 --> 00:00:50.630
imminent. It's right there, son.

00:00:50.640 --> 00:00:53.590
It's about to happen."I felt

00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:56.910
such an urgency and an anticipation for

00:00:56.920 --> 00:00:59.389
what God was telling me. He

00:00:59.399 --> 00:01:01.430
said, "There's an acceleration.

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:03.270
You're going to see

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:07.230
acceleration again from Passover

00:01:07.240 --> 00:01:09.550
going into the rest of the

00:01:09.550 --> 00:01:09.560
year."This

00:01:09.560 --> 00:01:11.710
will be a time of great

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:16.270
acceleration. So even from Rosh

00:01:16.270 --> 00:01:16.280
Hashanah,

00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:18.710
he said this would be a time

00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:22.469
of acceleration. But now he spoke

00:01:22.479 --> 00:01:26.469
to me and said from Passover to

00:01:26.469 --> 00:01:26.479
whenever—I

00:01:26.479 --> 00:01:27.950
don't know, he didn't give me a time

00:01:27.950 --> 00:01:27.960
frame—he

00:01:27.960 --> 00:01:30.109
just said this would be a time

00:01:30.119 --> 00:01:32.830
of even greater

00:01:32.840 --> 00:01:35.749
acceleration in the spirit realm,

00:01:35.759 --> 00:01:37.789
with the

00:01:37.799 --> 00:01:39.749
economy,

00:01:39.759 --> 00:01:42.350
signs, politics, all of

00:01:42.360 --> 00:01:44.670
it with Israel. Then he said this

00:01:44.680 --> 00:01:47.069
to me: "I want you to pay

00:01:47.079 --> 00:01:51.109
attention to the East."I saw

00:01:51.119 --> 00:01:54.270
Chicago and Philadelphia, and

00:01:54.280 --> 00:01:57.069
through the summer, I saw

00:01:57.079 --> 00:02:00.069
headlines in the news and

00:02:00.079 --> 00:02:05.149
great heatwaves

00:02:05.149 --> 00:02:05.159
in

00:02:05.159 --> 00:02:07.350
the

00:02:07.350 --> 00:02:07.360
Northeast—record

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:11.589
temperatures

00:02:11.599 --> 00:02:15.070
never seen before in that area. He said

00:02:15.080 --> 00:02:17.070
there will be record temperatures in

00:02:17.080 --> 00:02:19.710
Chicago and record temperatures in

00:02:19.720 --> 00:02:23.030
Philadelphia, and this would be a sign of

00:02:23.040 --> 00:02:25.270
the weather acceleration,

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:30.990
the birthing pains

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:33.990
of the earth, things like that.

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:39.550
I saw

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:44.509
heat like

00:02:44.519 --> 00:02:46.630
I hate because

00:02:46.640 --> 00:02:49.350
hot summers are terrible, but

00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:53.790
I saw a record-breaking summer up in Chicago.

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:55.910
I don't know if it's a day of

00:02:55.920 --> 00:02:58.830
heat or if it's a long stretch. I

00:02:58.840 --> 00:03:01.110
just saw that it would be

00:03:01.110 --> 00:03:01.120
record-breaking

00:03:01.120 --> 00:03:04.309
temperatures for the

00:03:04.319 --> 00:03:07.149
summer in that area—maybe

00:03:07.149 --> 00:03:07.159
it lasts

00:03:07.159 --> 00:03:09.229
a week, maybe it lasts a month.

00:03:09.239 --> 00:03:11.309
I just saw

00:03:11.319 --> 00:03:13.149
record-breaking temperatures

00:03:13.159 --> 00:03:16.869
over Philadelphia, New York, and all up in

00:03:16.869 --> 00:03:16.879
the

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:20.670
Northeast.

00:03:20.680 --> 00:03:23.509
Then he spoke to me about the

00:03:23.519 --> 00:03:26.830
thunderstorms again and told me there

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:31.190
would be record-breaking wind gusts. I saw

00:03:35.149 --> 00:03:35.159
downbursts

00:03:37.480 --> 00:03:39.429
coming out of the

00:03:39.429 --> 00:03:39.439
storms—updrafts

00:03:39.439 --> 00:03:41.830
and the wind coming down.

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:44.470
Straight-line

00:03:44.480 --> 00:03:50.229
winds over 150 mph.

00:03:50.239 --> 00:03:53.350
Not

00:03:53.350 --> 00:03:53.360
tornadic,

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:56.910
but like when a

00:03:56.920 --> 00:03:59.190
thunderstorm collapses and

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:02.149
has a burst

00:04:02.159 --> 00:04:06.229
of air. I saw 150 mph

00:04:06.229 --> 00:04:06.239
windbursts

00:04:06.239 --> 00:04:08.350
coming out like

00:04:08.350 --> 00:04:08.360
straight-line

00:04:08.360 --> 00:04:10.830
winds. The Lord was talking to me

00:04:10.840 --> 00:04:13.309
about storms coming in the spring,

00:04:13.309 --> 00:04:13.319
and

00:04:13.319 --> 00:04:16.990
like I told you,

00:04:16.990 --> 00:04:17.000
long-track

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:21.229
tornadoes.

00:04:21.229 --> 00:04:21.239
Pray—we

00:04:21.239 --> 00:04:23.390
have authority over this now. I'm not

00:04:23.400 --> 00:04:24.909
telling you all this to freak you

00:04:24.919 --> 00:04:27.230
out. There are storms we can pray

00:04:27.240 --> 00:04:29.629
against and pray a hedge of

00:04:29.639 --> 00:04:31.749
protection around your area,

00:04:31.759 --> 00:04:33.029
your

00:04:33.039 --> 00:04:35.710
neighborhood,

00:04:35.710 --> 00:04:35.720
and

00:04:35.720 --> 00:04:38.270
over

00:04:38.280 --> 00:04:40.870
your home. No

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:43.310
weapon formed against you will prosper.

00:04:43.320 --> 00:04:45.390
Psalms 91 and Psalms

00:04:45.390 --> 00:04:45.400
23—quoting

00:04:45.400 --> 00:04:47.710
those and getting ready

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:49.870
because we're in an active time

00:04:49.870 --> 00:04:49.880
on

00:04:49.880 --> 00:04:52.070
this earth. He started talking to

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:55.310
me about

00:04:55.310 --> 00:04:55.320
long-track

00:04:55.320 --> 00:04:59.670
supercells,

00:04:59.670 --> 00:04:59.680
superstorms

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:01.990
that were going to try to happen

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:04.790
in the spring through April, May,

00:05:04.790 --> 00:05:04.800
and

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:06.830
June.

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:09.310
We're almost there.

00:05:09.320 --> 00:05:10.230
I just thought it was interesting

00:05:10.230 --> 00:05:10.240
when

00:05:10.240 --> 00:05:11.909
he was talking to me about an

00:05:11.919 --> 00:05:14.029
acceleration at Passover because I was

00:05:14.039 --> 00:05:15.629
trying to figure out when Passover was.

00:05:17.199 --> 00:05:19.670
It's at the end of April.

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:23.150
That was

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:25.230
just one night of prayer. He

00:05:25.240 --> 00:05:27.749
started showing me glimpses of headlines:

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:30.749
glimpses of droughts in

00:05:30.759 --> 00:05:33.909
certain areas with no rain, and then

00:05:33.909 --> 00:05:33.919
for some areas,

00:05:33.919 --> 00:05:35.830
there was going to be a lot

00:05:35.840 --> 00:05:38.430
of rain in the spring.

00:05:38.440 --> 00:05:41.029
I saw great downpours,

00:05:41.039 --> 00:05:43.710
the lakes and ponds

00:05:43.720 --> 00:05:47.189
filling up as a sign of mercy. He started

00:05:47.199 --> 00:05:50.350
talking to me a lot about grace.

00:05:52.759 --> 00:05:55.110
It's something you don't earn; it's

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:57.510
something you don't deserve, but

00:05:57.520 --> 00:05:59.870
it's just by his love.

00:05:59.880 --> 00:06:02.749
He was

00:06:02.759 --> 00:06:05.110
really working on my heart

00:06:05.120 --> 00:06:08.870
about not being so rigid.

00:06:08.880 --> 00:06:10.950
He was saying,

00:06:10.960 --> 00:06:14.189
"Brandon, there is a balance

00:06:14.199 --> 00:06:18.350
where you are not living in sin,

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:22.070
but

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:25.749
you need to understand, son, that it's not

00:06:25.759 --> 00:06:29.510
about your works and never will

00:06:29.510 --> 00:06:29.520
be."Self-righteousness

00:06:29.520 --> 00:06:33.270
to him is a total

00:06:33.280 --> 00:06:35.909
stench. The Lord was

00:06:35.919 --> 00:06:39.230
correcting me because I'm not to be so focused

00:06:39.230 --> 00:06:39.240
on the

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:42.629
law. There's

00:06:42.639 --> 00:06:45.909
a balance where people can walk

00:06:45.919 --> 00:06:48.749
out grace.

00:06:48.759 --> 00:06:51.589
He washed all

00:06:51.599 --> 00:06:54.309
our sins away, past, present, and future,

00:06:54.319 --> 00:06:56.749
but it's not practicing a

00:06:56.759 --> 00:06:58.790
lifestyle of sin. I

00:06:58.790 --> 00:06:58.800
always

00:06:58.800 --> 00:07:01.430
want to

00:07:01.440 --> 00:07:03.790
come across in these videos

00:07:03.790 --> 00:07:03.800
as

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:06.469
a grace man too. I love the Lord

00:07:06.479 --> 00:07:08.909
with all my heart, and I

00:07:08.919 --> 00:07:11.869
want to make sure people understand that

00:07:11.879 --> 00:07:14.309
I don't want them to go to hell. I don't

00:07:14.319 --> 00:07:16.749
want them to think that they can

00:07:16.759 --> 00:07:19.790
live a life of sin and still

00:07:19.800 --> 00:07:21.469
make the Rapture.

00:07:26.759 --> 00:07:29.070
It's about relationship.

00:07:31.400 --> 00:07:33.189
I don't have all

00:07:33.199 --> 00:07:35.430
my stuff together,

00:07:35.440 --> 00:07:38.909
but

00:07:38.919 --> 00:07:41.270
where sin abounds,

00:07:41.280 --> 00:07:44.029
grace does much more abound.

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:48.110
I've been still praying for

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:51.390
the

00:07:51.390 --> 00:07:51.400
hostages'release.

00:07:51.400 --> 00:07:53.749
And I want to tell you all this: we need

00:07:53.759 --> 00:07:55.869
to be watching. I told you all when we

00:07:55.879 --> 00:07:57.670
saw that thing happen up in

00:07:57.670 --> 00:07:57.680
Kansas—those

00:07:57.680 --> 00:08:00.430
two kids doing

00:08:00.440 --> 00:08:03.029
what they did—that was part of what I

00:08:03.039 --> 00:08:05.149
told you and tried to warn you about,

00:08:05.159 --> 00:08:08.670
about parades and big concert events.

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:12.430
Be watchful, be prayed up, pray

00:08:12.430 --> 00:08:12.440
Psalm

00:08:12.440 --> 00:08:14.869
91. We

00:08:14.869 --> 00:08:14.879
can

00:08:14.879 --> 00:08:17.309
draw a bloodline

00:08:17.319 --> 00:08:20.430
and take authority

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:24.749
over the demonic agenda for mass shootings

00:08:24.749 --> 00:08:24.759
so

00:08:24.759 --> 00:08:26.950
that doesn't

00:08:26.960 --> 00:08:28.589
happen anymore. It's not just about

00:08:28.599 --> 00:08:31.189
America; it's a worldwide thing. I

00:08:31.199 --> 00:08:33.110
don't know if everybody has

00:08:33.110 --> 00:08:33.120
guns

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:36.469
everywhere, but I'm just saying to

00:08:36.469 --> 00:08:36.479
have

00:08:36.479 --> 00:08:40.469
wisdom and pray Psalm 91

00:08:40.479 --> 00:08:43.790
for protection over where you are at all

00:08:43.790 --> 00:08:43.800
times—malls,

00:08:43.800 --> 00:08:47.509
big gatherings,

00:08:47.519 --> 00:08:51.630
whatever. I just

00:08:51.640 --> 00:08:55.430
feel to pray over this

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:56.470
for

00:08:56.480 --> 00:09:00.990
protection because I saw

00:09:01.000 --> 00:09:02.310
a demonic

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:06.509
agenda coming to cause

00:09:06.519 --> 00:09:10.310
havoc and confusion.

00:09:10.320 --> 00:09:12.790
We have authority over this

00:09:12.800 --> 00:09:13.910
stuff.

00:09:13.920 --> 00:09:16.710
That

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:19.389
should not have happened in

00:09:19.399 --> 00:09:21.790
Kansas.

00:09:21.800 --> 00:09:24.389
We, as the body of

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:26.910
Christ, should start taking our dominion.

00:09:30.040 --> 00:09:33.269
We have massive warring angels.

00:09:35.399 --> 00:09:38.430
We're too devil-minded, thinking the

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:40.829
devil has power.

00:09:40.839 --> 00:09:44.150
No, we have

00:09:44.160 --> 00:09:46.790
power and authority. We shouldn't be

00:09:46.800 --> 00:09:49.150
letting the devil do anything. We have

00:09:49.160 --> 00:09:50.790
power and authority to tread on serpents

00:09:50.800 --> 00:09:53.509
and scorpions, and nothing shall by any

00:09:53.519 --> 00:09:55.829
means hurt you or your family.

00:09:58.440 --> 00:10:00.630
Every single day you wake up,

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:02.910
pray protection around your

00:10:02.920 --> 00:10:05.269
children—pray

00:10:05.279 --> 00:10:07.509
over them going to school

00:10:07.509 --> 00:10:07.519
or

00:10:07.519 --> 00:10:09.750
a

00:10:09.760 --> 00:10:13.509
basketball game. Pray a hedge

00:10:13.519 --> 00:10:16.590
of the blood of Jesus over your children,

00:10:16.600 --> 00:10:19.310
taking communion and

00:10:19.320 --> 00:10:21.069
anointing them. I got this oil

00:10:21.079 --> 00:10:23.150
from one of the people that

00:10:23.160 --> 00:10:24.269
follow

00:10:24.279 --> 00:10:27.829
us. He has an oil company here

00:10:29.959 --> 00:10:31.829
in America, and I think that's really

00:10:31.839 --> 00:10:34.190
cool. It's spikenard. He has all kinds of

00:10:34.200 --> 00:10:37.629
different fragrances like Rose

00:10:37.639 --> 00:10:39.590
of Sharon; I love them. But

00:10:39.590 --> 00:10:39.600
spikenard

00:10:39.600 --> 00:10:41.870
smelled

00:10:41.880 --> 00:10:44.150
really pretty. I

00:10:44.160 --> 00:10:46.190
anointed my kids with this. I

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:49.110
anoint them with oil.

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:50.590
He says he prays over these

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:53.030
oils, and

00:10:53.040 --> 00:10:54.750
I

00:10:54.760 --> 00:10:56.269
appreciate that.

00:10:58.880 --> 00:11:00.910
I anoint my kids and

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:07.350
anoint them with oil; I put a

00:11:07.360 --> 00:11:09.470
bloodline over them. I just

00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:10.750
go over there and put this on my

00:11:10.760 --> 00:11:13.269
finger

00:11:13.269 --> 00:11:13.279
and

00:11:13.279 --> 00:11:14.550
say, "In the name of

00:11:14.560 --> 00:11:16.310
Jesus, I put a bloodline over

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:18.550
you from the top of your head

00:11:18.550 --> 00:11:18.560
to

00:11:20.470 --> 00:11:20.480
the

00:11:20.480 --> 00:11:22.069
soles

00:11:22.079 --> 00:11:24.790
of your feet. No

00:11:24.800 --> 00:11:27.710
weapon formed against you will

00:11:27.710 --> 00:11:27.720
prosper."And

00:11:27.720 --> 00:11:30.150
every tongue that rises against you,

00:11:30.160 --> 00:11:31.949
we condemn it in the name of Jesus.

00:11:31.959 --> 00:11:34.230
I say there

00:11:34.230 --> 00:11:34.240
are

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:37.710
big angels

00:11:37.720 --> 00:11:39.990
with you wherever you

00:11:39.990 --> 00:11:40.000
go—on

00:11:40.000 --> 00:11:42.430
your right, your left,

00:11:42.440 --> 00:11:44.389
your back,

00:11:44.389 --> 00:11:44.399
and

00:11:44.399 --> 00:11:46.470
your

00:11:46.470 --> 00:11:46.480
front—with

00:11:46.480 --> 00:11:49.389
their swords and shields drawn

00:11:49.389 --> 00:11:49.399
so

00:11:49.399 --> 00:11:52.470
that nothing shall by any means hurt you.

00:11:54.839 --> 00:11:56.990
I anoint my house with oil, my

00:11:57.000 --> 00:11:59.790
car with oil, and the tires with oil.

00:11:59.790 --> 00:11:59.800
I've

00:11:59.800 --> 00:12:02.550
got oil streaks

00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:05.350
all over my doors because I make sure

00:12:05.360 --> 00:12:08.190
the blood of Jesus is applied over my

00:12:08.200 --> 00:12:10.509
house. No devil in hell

00:12:10.519 --> 00:12:13.150
can cross that bloodline.

00:12:20.320 --> 00:12:23.269
I believe

00:12:23.269 --> 00:12:23.279
in

00:12:23.279 --> 00:12:26.269
the protection and power

00:12:26.279 --> 00:12:29.550
of the blood of Jesus.

00:12:29.560 --> 00:12:31.870
I believe

00:12:31.880 --> 00:12:34.470
that

00:12:34.480 --> 00:12:38.189
Jesus's blood

00:12:38.189 --> 00:12:38.199
reigns

00:12:38.199 --> 00:12:41.910
supreme. No weapon formed against you or

00:12:41.920 --> 00:12:44.470
your family will prosper. And

00:12:44.480 --> 00:12:47.189
even if you are in those places where the

00:12:47.189 --> 00:12:47.199
devil is

00:12:47.199 --> 00:12:49.430
trying to do something,

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:51.949
you cause it to

00:12:51.959 --> 00:12:55.189
stop. You say, "No, cease and

00:12:55.189 --> 00:12:55.199
desist!

00:12:55.199 --> 00:12:58.389
You're maneuvering right now in the name

00:12:58.399 --> 00:13:02.189
of Jesus."No casualties.

00:13:02.199 --> 00:13:05.030
A thousand shall

00:13:05.040 --> 00:13:08.189
fall at my side and ten thousand at my right

00:13:08.199 --> 00:13:11.790
hand, but it will not come nigh us. I

00:13:14.160 --> 00:13:16.030
believe it with

00:13:16.030 --> 00:13:16.040
all

